THE life of the legendary actor Joe Mafela will be remembered today at the Joburg Theatre from 10am.Affectionately called Bra Joe, the actor died in a car accident on Saturday night. Family spokeswoman Millicent Mulelu said: &ldquo;The memorial service for my uncle will be held today at the Joburg Theatre in Braamfontein, Joburg. We will be celebrating our late uncle tomorrow and the service is open to the public.&rdquo; Millicent said details of the funeral will be shared at the memorial.